text.section:
Each administrative regulation shall state:
The place, time, and date of the scheduled public hearing;
The manner in which interested persons shall submit their:
Notification of attending the public hearing; and
Written comments;
That notification of attending the public hearing shall be transmitted to the administrative body no later than five (5) workdays prior to the date of the scheduled public hearing;
The deadline for submitting written comments regarding the administrative regulation in accordance with paragraph (c) of subsection (1) of this section; and
The name, position, address, and telephone and facsimile numbers of the person to whom a notification and written comments shall be transmitted.
